OL,3,CInside Italy's 'toxic town', where
OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,FIt is a feeling shared in Taranto, a
OL,7,Fsmall coastal city in Italy's south,
OL,8,Fwhere posters plastered on walls call
OL,9,Ffor "the monster" ` the nearby
OL,10,Fsteelworks ` to close.
OL,12,FCorby, Northamptonshire, and Taranto
OL,13,Fare more than 1,000 miles apart, but
OL,14,Ffamilies from both share similar
OL,15,Fstories and struggles.
OL,17,FAfter months of speaking online,
OL,18,Fcampaigners from both areas have met
OL,19,Ffor the first time to learn from each
OL,20,Fother.
