OL,3,CInside Italy's 'toxic town', where
OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,FAlison Gaffney and Andy Hinde's nine-
OL,7,Fyear-old son, Fraser, was diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith a rare form of blood cancer when
OL,9,Fhe was 17 months old.
OL,11,FHe was born in Corby, home to
OL,12,FBritain's biggest toxic waste scandal
OL,13,Fand the focus of the Netflix drama,
OL,14,FToxic Town.
OL,16,FThey believe waste that was
OL,17,Fnegligently moved around the town
OL,18,Fduring the steelworks reclamation
OL,19,Fcould have caused Fraser's condition.
