OL,3,CInside Italy's 'toxic town', where
OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,FThey travelled to Italy to meet
OL,7,Ffamilies who live alongside the
OL,8,FAcciaierie d'Italia plant, still known
OL,9,Flocally by its former name Ilva.
OL,11,FHere, children grow up talking about
OL,12,Fcancer.
OL,14,FManuela never got to meet her older
OL,15,Fsister. Miriam died aged five, a year
OL,16,Fafter being diagnosed with kidney
OL,17,Fcancer.
