OL,3,CInside Italy's 'toxic town', where
OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,FSpeaking to other families at the
OL,7,Fmeeting, Manuela said: "At the
OL,8,Fhospital in north Italy, the nurses
OL,9,Fwould ask, 'Where do you come from?'
OL,10,Fand then we said Taranto and they
OL,11,Fsaid, 'Of course.'
OL,13,F"They saw so many kids coming from
OL,14,Fhere to there. Many babies got sick
OL,15,Fbecause of this factory, and my mother
OL,16,Fis really, really mad."
OL,18,FAt this, Alison and Andy looked at
OL,19,Feach other, acknowledging that they
OL,20,Fhad heard something similar many times.
