OL,3,CInside Italy's 'toxic town', where
OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,FShe said: "We no longer have a need
OL,7,Ffor a steelworks. A steelworks that
OL,8,Fday by day, for decades, made us sick
OL,9,Fand killed us."
OL,11,FIn Corby, the town's main steelworks
OL,12,Fclosed in the early 80s. The largest
OL,13,Freclamation in Europe followed.
OL,15,FIn 2009, a High Court judge ruled that
OL,16,Fthe then-Corby Borough Council was
OL,17,Fresponsible for toxic waste being
OL,18,Fnegligently moved from the steelworks,
OL,19,Fcausing birth defects in 18 children.
