OL,11,FThyroid cancer is of particular
OL,12,Fconcern, says Valerio Cecinati,
OL,13,Fconsultant and Director of Paediatric
OL,14,FOncology.
OL,16,F"Now the question is not only how to
OL,17,Fcure a child with cancer, but why a
OL,18,Fchild has had childhood cancer," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
