OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,F"There is a clear link between the
OL,7,Fenvironment and the presence of
OL,8,Fchildhood cancer."
OL,10,FHe added: "In my opinion, it is
OL,11,Fimportant to study other diseases in
OL,12,Fchildhood that we have, like diabetes,
OL,13,Fepilepsy, because we have many studies
OL,14,Fthat begin to talk about the link."
OL,16,FIn Corby, some families are concerned
OL,17,Fabout where the waste was dumped and
OL,18,Fthe damage it could potentially still
OL,19,Fbe causing.
