OL,6,FA whistleblower, a contractor who
OL,7,Floaded the lorries at the time of the
OL,8,Freclamation, has told ITV News
OL,9,Fpreviously that it was dumped at sites
OL,10,Faround the area.
OL,12,FIn Taranto, a city with a population
OL,13,Fof 185,000, the steelworks is still
OL,14,Foperational.
OL,16,FIt has repeatedly been found to be in
OL,17,Fviolation of European environmental
OL,18,Frules and ordered to clean up its act.
OL,20,FProgress has been slow, much to the
OL,21,Fanger of those who live in its shadow.
