OL,3,CInside Italy's 'toxic town', where
OL,4,Cchildren grow up fearing cancer
OL,6,FIn the cemetery nearest Taranto's
OL,7,Fplant, once white statues have turned
OL,8,Fa shade of red. For Alison and Andy,
OL,9,Fit is a bleak reminder of home.
OL,11,FDuring Corby's reclamation, families
OL,12,Fspoke of seeing red dust around the
OL,13,Ftown, and they say it can still be
OL,14,Fseen when new building developments
OL,15,Fdisturb the land.
