OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "It is a strategic
OL,7,Fsite for steel production in Italy,
OL,8,Fand some people here really want to
OL,9,Fkeep it open because it gives jobs to
OL,10,Fmany."
OL,12,FThe Ilva plant has not responded to
OL,13,FITV News' request for a comment.
OL,15,FBut North Northamptonshire Council
OL,16,Fsaid in a statement: "We are currently
OL,17,Fverifying data regarding the number of
OL,18,Fchildhood cancer cases recorded for
OL,19,Fchildren living in Corby to understand
OL,20,Fwhether there are any potential cancer
OL,21,Fclusters.
