OL,6,F"This follows requests and concerns
OL,7,Ffrom members of the local community
OL,8,Fand we are keen to provide our
OL,9,Fsupport. Assessing the available data,
OL,10,Fensuring that it is accurate and
OL,11,Funderstanding what it shows is our
OL,12,Fpriority at this stage."
OL,14,FThe council added that it understands
OL,15,Fpeople are worried about potentially
OL,16,Fcontaminated land and that it will
OL,17,Fcontinue to review this.
OL,19,FFor Alison, it is about protecting
OL,20,Fpeople, more than anything else.
